description: Situated in one of South Boston’s most desirable neighborhoods, this well-maintained 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom condo offers a perfect blend of modern convenience and ideal location.  Enjoy close proximity to East Broadway’s vibrant shops and restaurants, the beach, and the Seaport District.  The residence features hardwood floors throughout, a beautifully updated kitchen with modern appliances, and an in-unit washer and dryer. Both bedrooms are generously sized, with the primary bedroom offering a spacious closet. Ample storage is available throughout the unit, enhancing everyday functionality.  Residents also benefit from a fully fenced, shared backyard—an excellent space for outdoor relaxation, grilling, or entertaining. The enclosed space offers added peace of mind for residents with children or pets.
